      <odd id="aspace_3f729e536af0d69245e985dc16af4cb5">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 27-H (YRG 27-H), Audio-visual materials and memorabilia documenting the Yale School of Medicine.</p>
      </odd>
