      <scopecontent id="aspace_3b4eaea4de596071ad18f48d6e79ddca">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The materials consist of audio recordings of symposia, programs, and other events held at the School of Medicine. Included are recordings of meetings of the Connecticut State Medical Society and Yale Medical Society, as well as Yale School of Medicine Alumni Day programs and the appointment of Fredrick Redlich as dean of the School of Medicine.</p>
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_99e977488807087af9ce13ea47703387">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged chronologically.</p>
      </arrangement>
